  "title": "HR Recruitment Intern [3/6 Months] (#HKN)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: Orchard/Somerset</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $10-$12</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>• Engage in full cycle of recruitment process from posting of job advertisements, sourcing, matching to onboarding of candidates.</p><p>• Handle candidates regarding their employment questions.</p><p>• Develop and manage the recruitment process for clients through sourcing, screening and qualifying candidates.</p><p>• Brief and prepare candidates for the interviews to assist candidates in securing the right jobs</p><p>• Adhoc HR admin functions</p><p>• Able to commit to 3/6 months</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>• Minimum A Levels or equivalent</p><p>• Good communication and interpersonal skills</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, please send your resume in Word document to clinicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg and cc <a href=\"mailto:kylie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>kylie@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></a></p><p><br /></p><p>Kylie Ng Kai Wi (R1104775) #HKN</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA Licence No: 99C4599</p><p>Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p>",
